Kintu Florence nke a makwaara dị ka Kintu Florence Tumwine (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 3 n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 1960) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Uganda

Ọ bụ nwanyị so na ndị omeiwu na-anọchite anya National Resistance Movement na ndị omebe iwu nke itoolu nke Uganda, Kalungu District.Kintu Florence makwaara dị ka Kintu Florence Tumwine (amụrụ 3 Eprel 1960) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Uganda
Ọ bụ nwanyị onye nnọchi anya nzuko omeiwu maka otu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị National Resistance Movement na nzuko omeiwu nke itoolu nke Uganda, Mpaghara Kalungu.
Kintu jere ozi dị ka onye isi oche na-anọchite anya Kalungu District tupu ọ banye n'ụlọ omebe iwu dị ka nwanyị omebe iwu ya wee hapụ ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na 2016 iji lekwasị anya na azụmaahịa ndị ọzọ.

Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị asọmpi asatọ gosipụtara mmasị ịnọ na National Resistance Movement (NRM) National Vice Chairperson Western Region position. Ụfọdụ n'ime ndị gosipụtara mmasị gụnyere onye bụbu ọnụ na-ekwuchitere ndị agha Col (Rtd) Shaban Bantariza, Dr

Emmanuel Diini Kisembo, onye bụbu onye omeiwu Busongora South Boaz Kafunda na ndị ọzọ. O meriri Matayo Kyaligonza na ntuli aka NRM maka ọkwa osote onyeisi oche mgbe ọ họọrọ ụdị nhọpụta site n'ọfịs NRM Electoral Commission na July 20, 2020. Na Machị 2022, a nabatara ya dị ka Onye isi oche Kọmitii Gọọmentị Obodo na Ọrụ Ọha.

Florence onye jere ozi dị ka minista nke ụlọ ọrụ ọdịbendị Obundhingiya Bwa Bwamba maka njem nleta na mmekọrịta ụlọ ọrụ, gbara arụkwaghịm na 2020 iji lekwasị anya na nkwado udo na mpaghara Rwenzori mgbe ọ rụchara ọrụ dị ka minisita ọdịbendị ruo afọ atọ. Kintu degaara praịm minista ụlọ ọrụ ahụ akwụkwọ ozi ọ gbara arụkwaghịm.
Ọ bụ onye isi oche mpaghara nke Rwenzori Women Peace Forum nke na-elekwasị anya na mpaghara ndị esemokwu agbụrụ metụtara.

Margaret Ntambaazi na Janat Nassiwa mere mkpesa megide Kintu na Ụlọikpe Kasị Elu. Ha kwuru na Kintu enweghị asambodo agụmakwụkwọ nke Ordinary na Advanced. Otú ọ dị, Justice Elizabeth Musoke jụrụ akwụkwọ mkpesa ntuli aka ahụ n'ihi na enweghị ihe akaebe siri ike iji gosi na e mebiri akwụkwọ agụmakwụkwọ Kintu. Mgbe ha nọ n'ụlọ ikpe dị elu, Caleb Alaka, Samuel Muyizzi, Ben Ikilai, na Julius Galisonga nọchitere anya Ntambaazi na Nassiwa, ebe Geoffrey Kandeebe nọchitere aha Kintu na Electoral Commission. Ntambaazi na Nassiwa kwere nkwa ime mkpesa megide mkpebi ahụ. Otú ọ dị, Kintu ruru eru zuru oke ma dị mma ka a họpụta ya dịka Justice Elizabeth Musoke na-achị.
